00:38:07.542 --> 00:38:09.125
I don't need your pity

00:38:10.625 --> 00:38:12.042
My bad for taking down your tyres

00:38:12.125 --> 00:38:13.042
I'll put them back on

00:38:13.125 --> 00:38:14.042
Whatever

