I knew in my life. I would never be good enough

00:44:36.458 --> 00:44:38.042
Coffee

00:44:38.125 --> 00:44:40.375
is probably my way of defiance

00:44:41.042 --> 00:44:44.708
What I didn't expect. is that coffee chose here

