00:45:27.792 --> 00:45:28.875
Not able to sleep?

00:45:28.958 --> 00:45:30.125
Ever since I decided to start my own business

00:45:30.208 --> 00:45:32.000
I have never had a good night's sleep

00:45:32.708 --> 00:45:35.500
