00:51:11.125 --> 00:51:14.208
We need the same spirit here as well!

00:51:15.417 --> 00:51:17.250
I know you all have deep feelings for tea

00:51:17.750 --> 00:51:18.875
I do. too

00:51:18.958 --> 00:51:21.333
